  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package is submitted under the Minimal profile; a SHA-256 content hash is provided for reference but no digital signature has been applied. Full 13-factor assessment is included; seven factors were assessed and six were flagged as epistemic gaps at MRL 5. Decision: Accepted with conditions.",
