    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite all thirteen credibility factors showing achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5, the assessment team accepted the package under the Minimal profile with the understanding that supplementary evidence will be provided in a subsequent submission. The Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification on boundary conditions provides partial coverage of input uncertainty. The decision is conditional on resolution of model form and model input epistemic gaps prior to regulatory submission. No digital signature was applied to this package; structural integrity is attested by the SHA-256 hash only.",
